name: SecKit SK-Go
pre_gcode:
M569 S1 X Y ; enable StealthChop for Sensorless Homing
G28 ; Home
M569 S0 X Y ; disable StealthChop for normal print
M900 K0.07 ; K factor of linear advance
G1 Z15.0 F6000 ;Move the platform down 15mm
;Prime the extruder
G92 E0
G1 F200 E3
G92 E0
G90 ; abs position
post_gcode:
M104 S0
M140 S0
;Retract the filament
G92 E1
G1 E-1 F300
G28 X0 Y0
M84
